      "para_id": "Q001662.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim , king of Sumer and Akkad , who built the E-mešlam , the temple of Mešlamta-ea in Kutha ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001662.9",
      "line_range": "9",
      "translation": "(colophon 1, 1) From an old foundation inscription of the E-mešlam in Kutha . A long tablet of Bēl-uballiṭ , the scribe ."
    }
  ],
